<header>
<div id="instruction">
	In what order do you think the candidate should perform these tasks after being given the discussion topic? Choose the right order.</div>
</header>
	
<section id="body">
  <img class="rightFloat" src="../media/LC_SP_004.JPG" mode="1" id="1001"/>
  <h7><p>In Part 2 of the IELTS Speaking Module you will be given a topic, time to think and make notes, then one to two minutes to talk.</p></h7>
  
  <p>Use your time to:</p>
  <ol id="questionList">
    <li>be clear about instructions;</li>
    <li>get your ideas in a logical order;</li>
    <li>have enough materials to speak until the examiner stops you.</li>
  </ol>
  
  <p><b>In what order should you perform these tasks in Part 2 of the Speaking Module?</b></p>
    <ol id="targetspotting">
		<list class="answerList">
		<li><a id="t1">Think  Speak  Write  Read</a></li>
    	<li><a id="t2">Think  Read  Speak  Write</a></li>
    	<li><a id="t3">Write  Read  Speak  Think</a></li>
    	<li><a id="t4">Write  Speak  Read  Think</a></li>
    	<li><a id="t5">Read  Write  Think  Speak</a></li>
    	<li><a id="t6">Read  Think  Write  Speak</a></li>
    	<li><a id="t7">Speak  Think  Read  Write</a></li>
    	<li><a id="t8">Speak  Write  Think  Read</a></li>
		</list>
	</ol>

</section>

